ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectCertain Participants in the 13th IAAF World Junior Championships Remission Order
PrecisCERTAIN PARTICIPANTS IN THE 13th IAAF WORLD JUNIOR CHMPIONSHIPS REMISSION ORDER, which grants remission of the $75 fee payable for the processing of an application for a single-entry temporary resident visa and of the $150 fee payable for a work permit to selected participants of the Championships which take place in Moncton, New Brunswick from July 19 to 25, 2010.
